&lt;/div&gt;</content></entry><entry gd:etag="W/&quot;DUENQ3c8eCp7ImA9WhBSEUQ.&quot;"><id>tag:blogger.com,1999:blog-3043523252258851613.post-3820271804181554728</id><published>2013-02-18T18:08:00.000+04:00</published><updated>2013-02-18T18:28:12.970+04:00</updated><app:edited xmlns:app="http://www.w3.org/2007/app">2013-02-18T18:28:12.970+04:00</app:edited><category scheme="http://www.blogger.com/atom/ns#" term="Java" /><category scheme="http://www.blogger.com/atom/ns#" term="Spring Framework" /><category scheme="http://www.blogger.com/atom/ns#" term="SOA" /><category scheme="http://www.blogger.com/atom/ns#" term="SCA" /><category scheme="http://www.blogger.com/atom/ns#" term="Oracle" /><category scheme="http://www.blogger.com/atom/ns#" term="Fusion Middleware" /><category scheme="http://www.blogger.com/atom/ns#" term="ESB" /><category scheme="http://www.blogger.com/atom/ns#" term="EIP" /><title>Пример разработки веб-сервиса по контракту с использованием Oracle SOA Suite и Spring Framework</title><link rel="replies" type="application/atom+xml" href="http://samolisov.blogspot.com/feeds/3820271804181554728/comments/default" title="Комментарии к сообщению" /><link rel="replies" type="text/html" href="http://samolisov.blogspot.com/2013/02/oracle-soa-suite-spring-framework.html#comment-form" title="Комментарии: 0" /><link rel="edit" type="application/atom+xml" href="http://www.blogger.com/feeds/3043523252258851613/posts/default/3820271804181554728?v=2" /><link rel="self" type="application/atom+xml" href="http://www.blogger.com/feeds/3043523252258851613/posts/default/3820271804181554728?v=2" /><link rel="alternate" type="text/html" href="http://samolisov.blogspot.com/2013/02/oracle-soa-suite-spring-framework.html" title="Пример разработки веб-сервиса по контракту с использованием Oracle SOA Suite и Spring Framework" /><author><name>Pavel Samolisov</name><uri>https://plus.google.com/108165051267137840220</uri><email>noreply@blogger.com</email><gd:image rel="http://schemas.g